snippet: The ensemble El Mundo presented some more variations on the chaconne, the classic Spanish dance, at Corpus Christi Church for the Music Before 1800 series.
abstract: Zachary Woolfe reviews program The Kingdoms of Castille: Spanish, Italian and Latin American Music, performed by El Mundo at Corpus Christi Church as part of the series Music Before 1800.
lead_paragraph: The ensemble El Mundo presented some more variations on the chaconne, the classic Spanish dance, at Corpus Christi Church for the Music Before 1800 series.
